Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把它放满整个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便签都放好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是七夕 拿便签有什么用啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以挂在许愿树上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:55.24,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(545,55)\fs15\be2\fad(200,0)}许愿树
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:55.24,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(545,115)\be2\fad(200,0)}将写上愿望的便签\N挂在这棵树上\N圣诞老人就会为你\N实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想为那些寻找救赎的人实现一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为圣诞礼物送给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:00:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现圣诞节的愿望 也是神明的工作啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:47.61,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}圣诞节当天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:47.72,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 虽然回收了便签…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中的要少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是免费实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是写上「想变成美女」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想变成有钱人」这类的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也无能为力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且名字都没写 怎么帮他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 还以为会人手不足特地多叫人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪学姐 知道委托人的便签 只有这两张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:18.60,SPEC3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,85)\fad(200,0)}请救救爸爸的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:18.60,SPEC3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,85)\fad(200,0)}急募女服务生！因为感冒店内人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助咖啡店和蛋糕店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就它们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个都帮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就兵分两路地去实现他们的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这俩店…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是正对着的两家店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说我们是竞争对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竞争对手？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一决胜负吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣 我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有人向我们提出比赛我们就不能退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有奖品的话应该会更有干劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}（奖品）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了就可以随便使唤他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…不是来实现愿望的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:22.00,SPEC4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,175)\fad(0,200)\frz5\fry-20\fs13\be2}爱丽丝咖啡店\N今日4时起包场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让这家店热闹起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美 美绪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 樱守祭那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要拯救这家咖啡店的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张便签…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但劳烦美绪大人大驾…诚惶诚恐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 真是家寒酸的店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思真是太破旧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才有复兴的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能输给对面的蛋糕店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉挺不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿成这样要干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦查啊侦查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能暴露身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们两个是恋人关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节这样才正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸红什么啊猪太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是装装样子罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 客人还不少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,价格适宜 种类丰富
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表也没什么缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:05:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键是味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 不愿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店不可小视啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你们是情侣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在举行情侣限定的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起吃这根巧克力棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在觉得是极限的地方停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据所剩的长度 我们将送上礼品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事谁会做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位是初次约会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话可能有点勉强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说不参加的话就不算情侣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我挑战吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先开始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一个圣诞蛋糕怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个好像都很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我蛋糕 还有烤猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢 谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到变态能量了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放弃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛啊 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂户同学 美绪学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}嘁 没想到会暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了 猪太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪学姐老是和太郎在一起 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面那家店着实是个强敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我想个好主意 现在马上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不讲理啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一杯本店推荐的王室奶茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 真是悠哉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 现在只能实行新菜单作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了都交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪大人亲手做的料理？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在这家店立马倒闭也无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼墨意面？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奶油蛋黄意面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧猪太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张嘴 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火山爆发！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在口中扩散开来的甘醇苦味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直刺舌头的香辛料的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是意面界的黑船开国啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪大人的…特制奶油蛋黄意面…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能把人感动到这份上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 这可是美绪大人亲手做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 爸爸也一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃得都晕过去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一个本店推荐的蛋糕怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 从现在开始咖啡半价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝赞限时优惠中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限时优惠 还真想得出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要超过他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西菜单里有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠这些就能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的东西全都2元出售
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限时优惠大抢购哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2元也太低了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里的东西就是客人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大卖一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2元也太犯规了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位注意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在买附赠美少女的魔法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 大家都在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变好吃 变好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你也跟着做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…变 变好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lovelove
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,spice！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我们也祭出王牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华丽地光临又小又脏的庶民小店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我也要…穿成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 就这样给我去拉男人去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪倒在我的魅力之下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 马上会被人家发现我是男生的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像还不太清楚自己的女装素质啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有男人会看穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一看啊看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多可爱的女生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚民们 尽情地崇拜我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是太丢人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就要输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只有这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟的 魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别限时优惠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟的诺亚也掀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此刺激强烈的风景…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没叫你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们也来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在是太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无权拒绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟的美腿让人忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝莉的腿也不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 这个女生更…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生好可怕好可怕好可怕好可怕 好可怕啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 终于结束了 结果到底是哪边赢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就不要提这个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺亚和大家在一起很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来辰吉人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已经关门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 有预约过4点开始的包场的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 包场？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是生日派对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是圣诞派对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的一个女生的生日和圣诞是同一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要作为生日来好好庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在开始做也赶不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 只能先道歉再拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日派对照常进行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要进行 绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 来做吧 派对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 庶民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辰…美小姐 料理拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里的准备就由我和结野来做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,间宫同学和柊学姐去买蛋糕来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday dear ——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——mio
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(341,328)}美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 能让他们高兴真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子看起来非常开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神的字典里没有不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday dear mio
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小满老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 一脸复杂的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天难道说 是石动学姐的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是美绪并不喜欢自己的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小时候开始就一个人过生日的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今年不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心愿吗 说不定其实就只是想和大家在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MM小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我忘了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点就在社团教室没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 之后就是如何不让学姐发现来准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石动学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 叶山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎他啊 说「今天因为那个贫乳累死了 真不爽」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争取时间 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚 刚才的是事实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 你这洗衣板少女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你没事乱来我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 是什么啊 那个胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 呀 没胸部的小美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也没有生气 所以站住 你这大变态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}绝对是骗人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.09,SPEC5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(356,109,345,83)\frz25}加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.09,SPEC5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(455,245,444,219)\frz25}还差一点了\N祝你好运！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你逃到哪里 都要把你抹杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}辰吉 快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经逃不掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认命吧 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老实实说出来不就好了 「是我生日」这几个字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很简单的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己的愿望都不能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又为什么要去实现别人的愿望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次每次 都是只关心别人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又不说关键的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在同在一个社团的份上 就听听你的遗言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 学姐你觉得我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话一直没有对学姐说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷 冷不防的说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个时候 说这种事 有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是 没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你 你 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:20:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能抓到我的话就来抓抓看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是到地狱的尽头 也不会放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 你这垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这臭猪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我费这么大工夫 你这臭垃圾变态猪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 是学姐的生日对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪太郎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家就想搞个惊喜派对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你可能不喜欢这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是学姐出生的 特别的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜 美绪姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是 这个该说是不一样呢 那个… 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:33.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:39.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快来一口气吹灭掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:40.96,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是主角的工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:48.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这之前还有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:55.61,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在灭掉蜡烛的火之前 要先把这东西的生命之火灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:21:59.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话很有趣呢 哈哈 哈哈 哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:00.91,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我是在开玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:04.24,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是喜日啊 喜日…
